== 市場行銷 ==
2014年6月13日，電影的首張劇照釋出，這透露了哈迪一人分飾兩角的邊疆區雙胞胎<ref>{{cite news|title=First Image of Tom Hardy and Tom Hardy as Twin Gangsters in Brian Helgeland’s LEGEND|url=http://collider.com/tom-hardy-legend-image/|accessdate=2014-06-13|newspaper=[[Collider|Collider]]|date=2014-06-13|archive-date=2014-06-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140615050705/http://collider.com/tom-hardy-legend-image|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="#1"/>。

==評價==
[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]有62%的評級，平均得分6／10；該網站共識：「作為一部黑幫傳記片，《金牌黑幫》有著重大的缺陷，但湯姆·哈迪的雙重角色演出毫不遜色，使其不辜負了它的片名」<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/legend_2015/ |title=Legend |work=[[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]] |publisher=[[Flixster|Flixster]] |accessdate=2015-11-10 |archive-date=2015-11-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151114061812/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/legend_2015 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]得分55，好壞平均參雜<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/legend |title=Legend |work=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]] |publisher=Metacritic |accessdate=2015-09-09 |archive-date=2015-09-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150912075249/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/legend |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

